Hi
After Update Nuget to Xamarin,forms 3.4,

UWP app'll be frozen (or it has been crashed?) after set the application.current.mainpage twice:
code here :

[MDXamarinSample.zip](https://github.com/xamarin/Xamarin.Forms/files/2593913/MDXamarinSample.zip)

No error can be catch
![qq 20181119134252](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/16309962/48688403-0c487e00-ec01-11e8-97a7-5331a55f9e42.jpg)

app.cs code:
`MainPage = new NavigationPage(new LoginPage());`

loginpage.cs code:
```
private void LoginBtn_Clicked(object sender, EventArgs e)
        {
            try
            {
                Application.Current.MainPage = new NavigationPage(new MainPage());
            }
            catch (Exception ex)
            {
                var eb = ex;
            }
        }
```
